    "This conclusion is supported by the comparison, where SVM with handcrafted features reported less favorable results compared to SVM with CNN.",
    "The unexpectedly superior performance of a shallow CNN architecture compared to deeper ones raised intriguing questions about the efficacy of deep models as well as TL.",
    "Despite these considerations, the work overall affirmed the feasibility of multilingual digit recognition through CNN-based approaches.The effectiveness of the CNN-SVM hybrid approach was further corroborated by the results of Parseh et al. [77].",
